  <fr:li>a type is <fr:em><fr:strong><html:span
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex>-1</fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:strong></fr:em> when it is a <fr:link
href="erct-001I.xml"
type="local"
addr="erct-001I">proposition</fr:link>;</fr:li>
  <fr:li>for <fr:tex>n  \geq  0</fr:tex>, a type <fr:tex>A</fr:tex> is <fr:em><fr:strong><html:span
xmlns:html="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"
style="white-space: nowrap"><fr:tex>n</fr:tex>-truncated</html:span></fr:strong></fr:em> when for every <fr:tex>x,y:A</fr:tex> the identification type <fr:tex>x=y</fr:tex> is <html:span
